message.body: Hey!!! I know you told me this like years ago but does Walgreen still do ink cartridges refills so I don 't have to buy a new ones?
Ohhh, I have no idea. I did go there before, but I haven't refilled an ink cartridge in years.
Oh have you just been buying them?
Yeah and if we need something big printed, I just ask my sister cause she does it at work.
I don't see why not though. My guess though is that not all of them do it. I went to the one on broad st. near me.
Where do you usually buy it from?
Anywhere. Target, Walmart, best buy, sometimes even cvs.
Do you know how much it usually costs?
No no don't be! Thank you!!! I'm probably going to go out to get it anyways so I'll know soon enough :)
